name: Cruise Intervals #4
description:
Today's session consists of 4 x 8-minute cruise intervals. Cruise intervals are performed within Zone 4. However, we are changing the target power throughout the effort. Some intervals increase, while others decrease in target power. Focus on controlled breathing and pedalling at a cadence similar to your Time Trial cadence.
